Radarpusht
============
A very simplistic Android APP that assumes the following goals:
- minimal battery usage
- very easy to operate - turn on, off, check the status of..

KML file for the cameras is available here: http://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-4181378,00.html

